---
title: header_construction (osaka-blocks)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_set_parent_hash : parent_hash = Hash32
    q_set_parent_hash --> q_set_ommers_hash : ommers_hash = Hash32
    q_set_ommers_hash --> q_set_coinbase : coinbase = Address
    q_set_coinbase --> q_set_state_root : state_root = Root
    q_set_state_root --> q_set_tx_root : transactions_root = Root
    q_set_tx_root --> q_set_receipt_root : receipt_root = Root
    q_set_receipt_root --> q_set_bloom : bloom = Bloom
    q_set_bloom --> q_set_difficulty : difficulty = Uint
    q_set_difficulty --> q_set_number : number = Uint
    q_set_number --> q_set_gas_limit : gas_limit = Uint
    q_set_gas_limit --> q_set_gas_used : gas_used = Uint
    q_set_gas_used --> q_set_timestamp : timestamp = U256
    q_set_timestamp --> q_set_extra_data : extra_data = Bytes
    q_set_extra_data --> q_set_prev_randao : prev_randao = Bytes32
    q_set_prev_randao --> q_set_nonce : nonce = Bytes8
    q_set_nonce --> q_set_base_fee : base_fee_per_gas = Uint
    q_set_base_fee --> q_set_withdrawals_root : withdrawals_root = Root
    q_set_withdrawals_root --> q_set_blob_gas_used : blob_gas_used = U64
    q_set_blob_gas_used --> q_set_excess_blob_gas : excess_blob_gas = U64
    q_set_excess_blob_gas --> q_set_parent_beacon : parent_beacon_block_root = Root
    q_set_parent_beacon --> q_set_requests_hash : requests_hash = Hash32
    q_set_requests_hash --> q_final : freeze(Header)
    q_final --> [*] : done

    note right of q_set_requests_hash
        INV: Header is slotted_freezable (immutable after construction).
        All 21 fields must be set in construction order.
    end note

    note right of q_set_difficulty
        INV: In PoS, difficulty is constant and nonce is zero.
        ommers_hash is always EMPTY_OMMER_HASH in post-merge forks.
    end note

    note right of q_set_base_fee
        INV: base_fee_per_gas follows EIP-1559 adjustment rules.
        blob_gas_used and excess_blob_gas follow EIP-4844 rules.
        requests_hash follows EIP-7685 computation.
    end note
